&lt;h3 id=&#34;b-also-estimate-the-complexity-order-o-of-procedure-a&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#b-also-estimate-the-complexity-order-o-of-procedure-a&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; b) Also estimate the complexity order ( O(...) ) of procedure A.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;note success&#34;&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;solution-2&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#solution-2&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; $solution:&lt;/h4&gt;
